Racdoor
=======

An SDK for producing haunted Ratchet & Clank (PS2) save games.

Building
--------

Only Linux-based build environments with the old homebrew compiler (e.g. ps2dev
version 1.2.0 with GCC 3.2.3) are supported. GNU Texinfo is required to build
the documentation.

To build the software:

	$ make

To build the documentation:

	$ make doc

